## Summary

- The **device control page** allows users to view and control devices, see energy consumption, and manage automation rules.
- The **trigger-value filter** on automation rules enables users to filter rules by specific trigger types and values.
- The system uses structured text files for data storage and retrieval.
- UI elements are identified by unique IDs for easy scripting and event handling.
- The backend logic parses files and filters data accordingly.

